Note that the mean impact is now 13290.1483 pipe feet rather than the 17075.1369 pipe feet of the "perfect sensor" solution.





\section Example3

The following example can be executed in the teva-sp/packages/sp/test
directory.  This one demonstrates the use of a robustness measure: "Tail
Conditional Expectation (TCE)."  This is the average of the worst k% 
of the events, where k is usually 5.  Note that evalsensor verifies that
we have found a better solution in terms of TCE, although the mean is 
slightly worse.

\verbatim
../../../bin/sp --path=../../../bin  --network=test1 --objective=ec_tce --ub=ns,5 --solver=heuristic

