This has reduced our running time by a factor of 5, and the TCE of the 
approximate solution is very close to the optimal value.  We may be more
aggressive still.  Let us raise the witness aggregation threshold to 0.25
(25 percent):

\verbatim
$ ../../../bin/sp --path=../../../bin  --path=../mod --network=test1 --objective
=ec_cvar --percent=ec,0.25 --ub=ns,5 --solver=pico


